			<ns0:name>pol...@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/101953680983947802512/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">The script to map gyp to scons already exists - see http://codereview.chromium.org/3431013/show.

We have reached out to one of the engineers recommended by BradN to help us add it as a step to the integration bot. He proposed to use hooks, but the resulting CLs added one for every time a update is done, not just in the integration bot. And even though in theory, if the DEPS has not changed running the script should be a no-op, in practice it might break something. This will affect all of the developers' clients and trybots. http://codereview.chromium.org/3432031/show

Jason is already looking into the bot setup. So he agreed to attempt to investigate how to add this as a step only to the bot. Hence, reassigning the bug.


